  "section_name": "Financial Analysis",
  "text": "EBITDA for Q3 2025 reached $10,040,000,000, translating to an EBITDA margin of 20.82%. Cash flow generation was exceptionally strong, with operating cash flow of $46,874,000,000 and free cash flow of $46,874,000,000, given zero capital expenditure for the quarter. This produced a free cash flow margin of 97.21%, indicating high cash conversion efficiency. The company also returned capital to shareholders through $5,300,000,000 in stock buybacks during Q3 2025.",
